  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2094390/extras/c0957d805dfb9a4219a315df9d9d0b40.avif?t=1673274514\" width=500 height=100 /></span><br>Doomed to dungeon laden with traps, you are doomed to rot and die.<br>It's up to you to be the first to escape the <strong>HELLPIT</strong>.<br>A 3rd person platformer featuring many unique obstacles and traps.<br>This game is balanced but don't be fool, this game can be hard and tricky.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2094390/extras/0a24000d4d30b8d00531a46a5f81cc9a.poster.avif?t=1673274514\" width=240 height=136 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2094390/extras/0a24000d4d30b8d00531a46a5f81cc9a.webm?t=1673274514\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2094390/extras/0a24000d4d30b8d00531a46a5f81cc9a.mp4?t=1673274514\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>  <strong>Simple mechanics</strong> - just hold <strong>W </strong> and jump<br></li><li>  <strong>Unique</strong> - No obstacles and traps layout are the same each time.<br></li><li>  <strong>Strategize</strong> - This is not straightforward game where you press 'W' key,<br>      You need to be good with your timing.<br></li><li>  <strong>Checkpoints</strong> - No save but checkpoints.<br>      Some obstacles are really hard to pass through.<br>      But when you made it, you feel like a boss.<br></li><li>  <strong>Hard but balanced </strong> - Unlike other rage game, this game designed is to be enjoyable challenge.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2094390/extras/41a83859fddcd1296330a4ffb0ca4eda.poster.avif?t=1673274514\" width=240 height=136 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2094390/extras/41a83859fddcd1296330a4ffb0ca4eda.webm?t=1673274514\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2094390/extras/41a83859fddcd1296330a4ffb0ca4eda.mp4?t=1673274514\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2094390/extras/d3924810c1e912a6d528148b1dc524d5.poster.avif?t=1673274514\" width=240 height=136 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2094390/extras/d3924810c1e912a6d528148b1dc524d5.webm?t=1673274514\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2094390/extras/d3924810c1e912a6d528148b1dc524d5.mp4?t=1673274514\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2094390/extras/931ddfed0367425a29c8dc6c8e27a830.poster.avif?t=1673274514\" width=240 height=136 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2094390/extras/931ddfed0367425a29c8dc6c8e27a830.webm?t=1673274514\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2094390/extras/931ddfed0367425a29c8dc6c8e27a830.mp4?t=1673274514\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2094390/extras/c0957d805dfb9a4219a315df9d9d0b40.avif?t=1673274514\" width=500 height=100 /></span><br>Doomed to dungeon laden with traps, you are doomed to rot and die.<br>It's up to you to be the first to escape the <strong>HELLPIT</strong>.<br>A 3rd person platformer featuring many unique obstacles and traps.<br>This game is balanced but don't be fool, this game can be hard and tricky.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2094390/extras/0a24000d4d30b8d00531a46a5f81cc9a.poster.avif?t=1673274514\" width=240 height=136 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2094390/extras/0a24000d4d30b8d00531a46a5f81cc9a.webm?t=1673274514\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2094390/extras/0a24000d4d30b8d00531a46a5f81cc9a.mp4?t=1673274514\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>  <strong>Simple mechanics</strong> - just hold <strong>W </strong> and jump<br></li><li>  <strong>Unique</strong> - No obstacles and traps layout are the same each time.<br></li><li>  <strong>Strategize</strong> - This is not straightforward game where you press 'W' key,<br>      You need to be good with your timing.<br></li><li>  <strong>Checkpoints</strong> - No save but checkpoints.<br>      Some obstacles are really hard to pass through.<br>      But when you made it, you feel like a boss.<br></li><li>  <strong>Hard but balanced </strong> - Unlike other rage game, this game designed is to be enjoyable challenge.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2094390/extras/41a83859fddcd1296330a4ffb0ca4eda.poster.avif?t=1673274514\" width=240 height=136 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2094390/extras/41a83859fddcd1296330a4ffb0ca4eda.webm?t=1673274514\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2094390/extras/41a83859fddcd1296330a4ffb0ca4eda.mp4?t=1673274514\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2094390/extras/d3924810c1e912a6d528148b1dc524d5.poster.avif?t=1673274514\" width=240 height=136 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2094390/extras/d3924810c1e912a6d528148b1dc524d5.webm?t=1673274514\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2094390/extras/d3924810c1e912a6d528148b1dc524d5.mp4?t=1673274514\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2094390/extras/931ddfed0367425a29c8dc6c8e27a830.poster.avif?t=1673274514\" width=240 height=136 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2094390/extras/931ddfed0367425a29c8dc6c8e27a830.webm?t=1673274514\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2094390/extras/931ddfed0367425a29c8dc6c8e27a830.mp4?t=1673274514\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
